                    <p>Developed by <a href="https://twitter.com/rutoruz">rutoru</a>. Code released under the <a href="https://github.com/rutoru/Runa-CCA/blob/master/LICENSE">MIT License</a>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

